c Skills List<\/strong> (MLTSSL) includes <strong>212 occupations<\/strong> and is prescribed under Legislative Instrument <a class=\"uline\" href=\"https:\/\/www.legislation.gov.au\/F2019L00278\/latest\/text\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">LIN 19\/051<\/a> <i class=\"icon-tiny fa fa-external-link\"><\/i>.<\/p>\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 10px;\">The MLTSSL is relevant to applicants who are invited to apply for the following visas:<\/p>\n<ul style=\"margin-bottom: 15px;\">\n<li><a class=\"uline\" href=\"https:\/\/www.anzscosearch.com\/skilled-independent-189-visa\/\">Subclass 189 (Skilled Independent)<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a class=\"uline\" href=\"https:\/\/www.anzscosearch.com\/skilled-nominated-190-visa\/\">Subclass 190 (Skilled nominated)<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a class=\"uline\" href=\"https:\/\/www.anzscosearch.com\/skilled-work-regional-491-visa\/\">Subclass 491 (Skilled Work Regional (Provisional)<\/a> (Family sponsored))<\/li>\n<li>Subclass 491 (Skilled Work Regional (Provisional) (State or Territory government agency nominated))<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 10px;\">The MLTSSL is also relevant to applicants applying for the:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><a class=\"uline\" href=\"https:\/\/www.anzscosearch.com\/skilled-graduate-485-visa\/\">Subclass 485 (Temporary Graduate)<\/a> visa (Post-Vocational Education Work stream)<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/div>\n[\/vc_column_text][vc_column_text][\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column_inner][\/vc_row_inner][\/vc_column][vc_column column_padding=&#8221;no-extra-padding&#8221; column_padding_tablet=&#8221;inherit&#8221; column_padding_phone=&#8221;inherit&#8221; column_padding_position=&#8221;all&#8221; flex_gap_desktop=&#8221;10px&#8221; column_element_direction_desktop=&#8221;default&#8221; column_element_spacing=&#8221;default&#8221; desktop_text_alignment=&#8221;default&#8221; tablet_text_alignment=&#8221;default&#8221; phone_text_alignment=&#8221;default&#8221; background_color_opacity=&#8221;1&#8243; background_hover_color_opacity=&#822